# Requirements

## Hardware Requirements
- Processor: Intel Core i3 or above
- RAM: 4 GB minimum (8 GB recommended)
- Storage: 2 GB free disk space
- Operating System: Windows 10/11, macOS, or Linux

## Software Requirements
- Python 3.10 or above
- Visual Studio Code (or any Python IDE)
- Git (optional)
- Web Browser (Chrome, Edge, or Firefox)

## Python Libraries
Install the required packages using:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Required libraries:
- streamlit
- pandas
- numpy
- scikit-learn
- joblib
- matplotlib
- seaborn
- nltk
- spacy
- requests

## Dataset
- Career recommendation dataset (CSV format)
- User skills, interests, education, and career information

## Features
- User Registration/Login (optional)
- Skill and Interest Analysis
- Career Recommendation using Machine Learning
- Career Information Display
- User-Friendly Dashboard